request for more
YOUR SERVICE.
Mr. Emmanuel Johnson

Dear Valued Customer,
We have received your message regarding the immediate payment of your fund of US$10.5 million. We are pleased to inform you that all necessary arrangements have been made for the immediate disbursement of your funds to you.
We offer three major modes of disbursing funds to our clients, and you are expected to choose the best option that suits you. The options are:
1. Certified bank draft which will be delivered to your address by an approved courier service. This option will cost you only $500 including insurance.

Kindly choose from the above-listed options on the mode which you wish to receive your funds. Once we receive your payment, we will immediately disburse your funds to you.
Thank you for choosing JP Morgan Chase Bank.
Sincerely,
Mr.
Best wishes,
Paula
